# A short bilingual practice story with the new family cast.

title: 一起玩 (Let's Play Together)
scene: park

GRACE walks in from left
GRACE (happy): 你好！我是 Grace。
GRACE: Hello! I am Grace.

ELLIOTT runs in from right
ELLIOTT (happy): 我是 Elliott。我们一起玩吧！
ELLIOTT: I am Elliott. Let's play together!

LEAH walks in from left
LEAH (surprised): 球！
LEAH: Ball!

GRACE points
ELLIOTT jumps
LEAH laughs

GRACE (happy): 玩得开心！
ELLIOTT waves
LEAH waves
GRACE: Have fun!
